Usage: flipSdpObject [-help] -object {objName(s)} [-x  | -y ]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-object {objName(s)}     # Name(s) of object to be flipped (string, required)
-x                       # flip x direction, default is y (bool, optional)
-y                       # flip y direction, default flip Y (bool, optional)